Module com.example.project3
Package com.example.project3

Class FitnessClass

java.lang.Object
com.example.project3.FitnessClass
public class FitnessClass
extends java.lang.Object
The FitnessClass class represents the fitness classes at the gym. Each FitnessClass object includes the name of the class, the name of the instructor, the time of the class, and a list of members who are checked in at the current time. This class also includes methods to add or drop a class, and to check if a member is checked into the class.
Author:
Jackson Lee, Serena Zeng
